  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Rooms in the hotel are equipped with bathroom, flat screen TV, hairdryer and safe.</li>
<li>Peaceful twin or double rooms (please specify preference when booking) are located at the rear of the property with views overlooking the forest whilst larger rooms, sleeping up to 3 adults, are located at the front of the property, with balcony and wonderful views.</li>
</ul>
<p>Accommodation summary</p>
<p>Hotel:</p>
<ul>
<li>Twin (A2), private bath, Forest view</li>
<li>Twin (B3), private bath, balcony, valley view</li>
 </ul>
<p>Apartments:</p>
<ul>
<li>Two Room Apartment, 34m², (C4), double bedroom, living area with double sofa bed, bathroom and balcony, valley view</li>
<li>Three Room apartment, 53m², (D6),  2 x double/twin bedroom, living area with double sofa bed, bathroom and balcony, valley view</li>
<li>Four Room Apartment, 78m² ,(E8), 2 x double/twin bedroom with shared bathroom and WC, 1 x double/twin bedroom with ensuite bath, living area with double sofa bed, bathroom and balcony, valley view</li>
<li>Five Room Apartment 100m² (F0),2 x double/twin bedroom with shared bathroom and WC, 2 x double/twin bedroom with shared bathroom, living area with double sofa bed, bathroom and balcony, valley view</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<ul>
<li>Both hotel rooms and apartments have access to Wi-Fi.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
